                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         +
 Full Linux containers, running on Android core smartphones globally. The biggest upgrade to Acurast since the TGE launch in January.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    +
